{"date":"2009-07-04","platform":"TV","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/72/83/1761_9qvv3.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/72/83/1761_9qvv3.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/72/83/1761_9qvv3.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/72/83/1761_9qvv3.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/72/83/1761_9qvv3.jpg"},"summary":"元素消失！未来委托给了我们！\r\n2029年，在地中海沿岸发生了大规模的陆地下陷现象。直径达3千米的氧元素突然从地壳中消失了。从那以后，地球上各种元素陆陆续续都消失了。\r\n元素的消失，导致森林田地、建筑物和古代遗迹，甚至连生命也消逝了。\r\n人类深怀痛感。“万物因元素存在”。\r\n从那一天过了60年，人口比起最盛期已经减少到了十分之一。\r\n拼命调查研究的结果判明了消失的元素的去向。原来元素流入了次元之壁另一端的另一个地球“负地球”中。\r\n赌上地球的存亡，建立了名为“元素猎人”的组织。成员全部是13岁以下的孩子。能够联系上内加亚斯的，仅限于脑组织比大人柔软的小孩……\r\n","name":"エレメントハンター","name_cn":"元素猎人","tags":[{"name":"元素猎人","count":28,"total_cont":0},{"name":"我天朝可引进","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"化學","count":16,"total_cont":0},{"name":"NHK教育","count":13,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009年7月","count":12,"total_cont":0},{"name":"元素周期表","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"化学","count":10,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"TV","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"教育","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"科教","count":7,"total_cont":0},{"name":"动画","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"口袋暴龙","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日本动画","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"化学片","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"荒川稔久","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"2009年","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"子供向","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"日番","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"本城雄太郎","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"NHKエンタープライズ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"数码妖怪","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"榎本温子","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"アニメ","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"奇幻","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"SF","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"第一季","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"NHKEnterprises、HeewonEntertain","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"in